---
title: Southeast Asian Coconut Beef Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Veggies
description: Make a simple stir-fry a little more special by serving with mouth-watering garlic rice! Add a twist of coconut milk and our Southeast Asian spice blend for a big helping of flavour with minimal effort. Enjoy your tasty and colourful creation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southeast-asian-coconut-beef-stir-fry-e6ca8b9a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/southeast-asian-coconut-beef-stir-fry-5f7e60fdba59155848207ea9-a7b8af4e.pdf
author: HelloFresh
